Basic Usage Instructions
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    
Dev:
1. virtualenv: cosy_env (piprequirements.in)
2. virtual host: N/A
3. github: https://github.com/jobcpf/cosy (jobcpf/cosy)
4. auto production/staging settings: script/deploy.cfg

